metadata.name: MPower
metadata.description:
MPower, 2021
Digital Art Composite

Original Photo, 2012
Sebring, Florida
12 Hours of Sebring

The original image was captured in March of 2012 at the ‘12 Hours of Sebring’ auto race with a Nikon D300s using a Nikkor 70-200m f/2.8 lens. 

In December of 2021, I pulled the original NEF raw image from the archives and turned it into a mixed media piece of art. The image was processed over a couple of hours to give a look and feel of being sketched by hand (which partially is). Four versions were created with different background colors to match the BMW M Power logo and a GIF was created for viewing pleasure. 

A full description of this NFT can be found here: [https://abromphoto.com/nft](https://abromphoto.com/nft)
